SUBSTITUTE FOR
SENATE BILL NO. 685
A bill to amend 1994 PA 451, entitled
"Natural resources and environmental protection act,"
(MCL 324.101 to 324.90106) by adding section 36109b.
THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF MICHIGAN ENACT:
1 Sec. 36109b. The owner of farmland and related buildings
2 subject to a conservation easement described in section 2141 and to
3 a development rights agreement under section 36104, a purchase of
4 development rights or agricultural conservation easement under
5 section 36111b, or an agricultural conservation easement under
6 section 36206 may claim a credit under section 36109 if the
7 conservation easement described in section 2141 and the development
8 rights agreement, purchase of development rights, or agricultural
9 conservation easement were executed before January 1, 2025.
